# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:16
translate malay e02s04_fa7cdc9b:

    # mc "How much?"
    mc "Berapa?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:17
translate malay e02s04_cba3e59a:

    # mc "Come on, how much?"
    mc "Marilah, berapa?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:20
translate malay e02s04_c9c374c5:

    # mh "I am not going to bother answering that. It is really a silly question."
    mh "Aku tak akan menjawabnya. Ianya soalan yang bodoh."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:23
translate malay e02s04_a4c2d21c:

    # mc "But I'm curious. Would you represent me in court for free, or would I have to pay you?"
    mc "Tapi aku nak tahu. Kau akan mewakili aku di mahkamah secara percuma, atau aku kena bayar kau?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:26
translate malay e02s04_446acdeb:

    # mh "Of course I would do it pro-bono, [mcname]."
    mh "Sudah tentu aku akan lakukannya secara pro-bono, [mcname]."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:29
translate malay e02s04_80cc9f92:

    # mc "That means for free right?"
    mc "Maksudnya percuma kan?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:32
translate malay e02s04_d09871a8:

    # mh "Yes. But we do not have to worry about me representing you because you will not be committing any crimes, correct?"
    mh "Ya. Tapi kami tak perlu risau tentang aku wakilkan kau sebab kau tak lakukan apa-apa jenayah, betul?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:35
translate malay e02s04_0cb50db4:

    # mc "Of course not, but I'm glad to know you'd be in my corner."
    mc "Sudah tentu tak, tapi aku gembira tahu yang kau akan berada di sudut aku."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:36
translate malay e02s04_cf37f363:

    # mc "Maybe I should try that out - being in your corner, I mean. During a trial."
    mc "Mungkin aku patut mencubanya - berada di sudut kau, maksud aku. Semasa perbicaraan."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:37
translate malay e02s04_42507f38:

    # mc "Are you hiring?"
    mc "Kau masih lagi mencari pekerja?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:40
translate malay e02s04_ee087b37:

    # mh "I always keep my eyes open for talent."
    mh "Aku sentiasa membuka mata aku untuk bakat."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:43
translate malay e02s04_40b79f60:

    # mc "Well there is no one more talented than me. And we work so well together in the bedroom. Just imagine what we could do outside of it."
    mc "Tak ada yang lebih berbakat daripada aku. Dan kita bekerja dengan baik di dalam bilik tidur. Bayangkan apa yang boleh kita lakukan di luar daripada itu."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:46
translate malay e02s04_8f355e21:

    # mh "I do not need to imagine. We are out of the bedroom as often as we are in it."
    mh "Aku tak perlu membayangkan. Kita keluar dari bilik tidur sekerap kita berada di dalamnya."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:50
translate malay e02s04_debd7d22:

    # mc "Ha! True. {w}Still, what if I was interested in pitching in?"
    mc "Ha! Betul. {w}Namun, macam mana kalau aku berminat untuk menyertainya?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:53
translate malay e02s04_17707427:

    # mh "I think you are pulling my leg."
    mh "Aku rasa kau bergurau."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:56
translate malay e02s04_27c6e311:

    # mc "Come on, I've always liked the law."
    mc "Marilah, aku sentiasa menyukai undang-undang."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:59
translate malay e02s04_d792eb3d:

    # mh "[mcname] I love you, but liking the law and applying yourself to it are two {i}very{/i} different things."
    mh "[mcname] Aku sayangkan kau, tapi menyukai undang-undang dan mengamalkannya adalah dua perkara yang {i}sangat{/i} berbeza."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:60
translate malay e02s04_bef7a842:

    # mh "And you would need a lot of experience before working in any office."
    mh "Dan kau perlukan banyak pengalaman sebelum bekerja di mana-mana pejabat."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:63
translate malay e02s04_427cce14:

    # mc "Even if I have an {i}in{/i} with a kickass lawyer?"
    mc "Walaupun aku {i}sesuatu{/i} dengan peguam yang hebat?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:67
translate malay e02s04_cdd817d4:

    # mh "Flattery works in bed, but it will not get you into my office."
    mh "Sanjungan berfungsi di atas katil, tapi ia tak akan membawa kau ke pejabat aku."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:71
translate malay e02s04_50dcb3f4:

    # mc "Just think about it. I could be your sexy intern, bending over a file cabinet."
    mc "Bayangkan. Aku boleh jadi pelatih seksi kau, membongkok di atas kabinet fail."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:72
translate malay e02s04_589acb0b:

    # mc "Giving you a massage whenever your shoulders need a little rubbing..."
    mc "Berikan kau urutan bila-bila masa bahu kau memerlukan sedikit gosokan..."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:75
translate malay e02s04_06a5d34c:

    # mh "You're already defeating your case, Mister. I would never get any work done."
    mh "Kau dah mengalahkan kes kau, tuan. Aku tak akan menyelesaikan apa-apa kerja."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:78
translate malay e02s04_bc692d24:

    # mc "Hahaha. Can't blame a guy for trying."
    mc "Hahaha. Tak boleh salahkan aku kerana mencuba."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:89
translate malay e02s04_photo_845c4c57:

    # mc "What was that?"
    mc "Apakah itu tadi?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:92
translate malay e02s04_photo_4dcc526a:

    # mh "Over there. That couple just took a picture of us."
    mh "Di sana. Pasangan itu baru ambil gambar kita."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:95
translate malay e02s04_photo_bbdf5b32:

    # mh "Excuse me, did you want something? A picture perhaps?"
    mh "Maaf, awak nak sesuatu? Gambar mungkin?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:99
translate malay e02s04_photo_8831022a:

    # ap "Oh I'm so sorry. My wife asked to take a photo of her but my aim was off."
    ap "Oh saya minta maaf. Isteri saya meminta untuk mengambil gambarnya tapi sasaran saya meleset."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:101
translate malay e02s04_photo_5ae2f27f:

    # atp "Hmmph. Yes, that's what happened."
    atp "Hmmph. Ya, itulah yang berlaku."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:102
translate malay e02s04_photo_f432e7b9:

    # ap "Angela, stop."
    ap "Angela, berhenti."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:110
translate malay e02s04_photo_8c26cb31:

    # mc "What's going on?"
    mc "Apa yang sedang berlaku?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:113
translate malay e02s04_photo_a6c28f39:

    # atp "Relax. It was nothing sinister. We, uh, couldn't help but overhear your conversation."
    atp "Bertenang. Ia bukan sesuatu yang jahat. Kami, eh, tak dapat menahan diri daripada mendengar perbualan awak."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:115
translate malay e02s04_photo_e4002560:

    # ap "Can you..."
    ap "Boleh awak..."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:117
translate malay e02s04_photo_3135da05:

    # atp "Oh, grow up, Alexander."
    atp "Oh, membesarlah, Alexander."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:120
translate malay e02s04_photo_97733348:

    # mh "Wait, I recognize you. {w}Alexander Portillo, Channel Six, right?"
    mh "Tunggu, saya kenal awak. {w}Alexander Portillo, Saluran Enam, bukan?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:123
translate malay e02s04_photo_05f710da:

    # ap "Oh, uh-huh. Yes. I didn't imagine you'd recognize me. This is my wife, Angela."
    ap "Oh, uh huh. ya. Saya tak sangka awak akan mengenali saya. Ini isteri saya, Angela."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:125
translate malay e02s04_photo_e7da310f:

    # atp "And you are Melissa Harris."
    atp "Dan awak adalah Melissa Harris."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:128
translate malay e02s04_photo_a2b13b41:

    # mh "Pleased to meet you. This is my boyfriend, [mcname]. Now can you delete that photo?"
    mh "Gembira bertemu dengan awak. Ini teman lelaki saya, [mcname]. Sekarang boleh awak padamkan foto itu?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:131
translate malay e02s04_photo_85e6258a:

    # ap "So strict. It's not illegal to snap a few shots on vacation."
    ap "Tegasnya. Tak salah untuk mengambil beberapa gambar semasa bercuti."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:134
translate malay e02s04_photo_9d06fa20:

    # mh "Then perhaps you could explain why you took a picture of us."
    mh "Kalau macam itu mungkin awak boleh jelaskan kenapa awak ambil gambar kami."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:142
translate malay e02s04_photo_f63d5142:

    # ap "There, it's gone."
    ap "Dah dipadam."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:145
translate malay e02s04_photo_a73f30b7:

    # atp "And we're terribly sorry for disturbing you."
    atp "Dan kami amat kesal kerana mengganggu awak."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:148
translate malay e02s04_photo_9dc3bfdf:

    # mh "So, what was this? You were going to post a scoop of me while I'm on vacation?"
    mh "Jadi, apakah ini? Awak akan buat berita daripada saya semasa saya bercuti?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:151
translate malay e02s04_photo_7798498a:

    # atp "Hahaha. I'd have to be pretty desperate to try selling that. No offense."
    atp "Hahaha. Saya perlu sangat terdesak untuk mencuba menjualnya. Jangan terasa."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:152
translate malay e02s04_photo_38b50f82:

    # atp "You're a banging lawyer, but do you think anyone would care to find out that you summer up in the mountains?"
    atp "Awak seorang peguam yang terbaik, tapi awak ada fikir sesiapa akan mengambil berat untuk mengetahui yang awak sedang bercuti di pergunungan?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:155
translate malay e02s04_photo_9cdfd432:

    # ap "Please excuse us, we were just excited and-"
    ap "Tolong maafkan kami, kami hanya teruja dan-"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:158
translate malay e02s04_photo_7bf185d4:

    # atp "Not excited, just bored. We've skied and skied and then we noticed you and..."
    atp "Tak teruja, cuma bosan. Kami dah bermain ski dan kemudian kami perasan awak dan..."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:159
translate malay e02s04_photo_781f3ba4:

    # atp "Well you and I are like two peas in a pod, Ms. Harris."
    atp "Baiklah awak dan saya macam pelanduk dua serupa, Cik Harris."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:162
translate malay e02s04_photo_cb8e98cf:

    # mh "Two peas in a pod? {w}What do you mean by that?"
    mh "Pelanduk? {w}Apa awak maksudkan dengan itu?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:165
translate malay e02s04_photo_84bb0e2c:

    # ap "Listen, we're really sorry for bothering you. We should go."
    ap "Dengar, kami betul-betul minta maaf kerana mengganggu awak. Kami patut pergi."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:168
translate malay e02s04_photo_57a303eb:

    # atp "You're just as curious as I am, Alexander."
    atp "Kau juga ingin tahu macam aku, Alexander."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:169
translate malay e02s04_photo_35fd49b3:

    # atp "You're transgender right?"
    atp "Awak transgender kan?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:173
translate malay e02s04_photo_aafe8056:

    # ap "Angela!"
    ap "Angela!"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:175
translate malay e02s04_photo_58513a00:

    # atp "What?"
    atp "Apa?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:178
translate malay e02s04_photo_1ed9e342:

    # ap "That is inappropriate!"
    ap "Itu tak sesuai!"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:180
translate malay e02s04_photo_c2712e6d:

    # atp "Oh, come on."
    atp "Oh, marilah."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:183
translate malay e02s04_photo_7102307b:

    # mh "I am. Is that why you were taking photos of me?"
    mh "Betul. Itulah sebabnya awak mengambil gambar saya?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:186
translate malay e02s04_photo_79cc4def:

    # atp "No. Well, it's... I mean it's really kind of a funny story."
    atp "Tak. Jadi, itu... maksud saya ia sebenarnya cerita yang kelakar."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:188
translate malay e02s04_photo_07644846:

    # ap "I think Angela just panicked."
    ap "Saya rasa Angela hanya panik."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:191
translate malay e02s04_photo_0bb4aecf:

    # atp "I did not panic. I just... well, I thought it was you but I didn't know it was you."
    atp "Saya tak panik. Saya cuma... baiklah, saya fikir itu awak tapi saya tak tahu itu adalah awak."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:192
translate malay e02s04_photo_39efc70a:

    # atp "But {i}then{/i} I realized it was you and I thought..."
    atp "Tapi {i}kemudian{/i} saya sedar itu awak dan saya fikir..."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:193
translate malay e02s04_photo_1b1c21ae:

    # atp "{i}But{/i} you're on vacation and I didn't want to bother you but I've wanted to meet you so I told Alexander to get your attention."
    atp "{i}Tapi{/i} awak sedang bercuti dan saya tak nak menyusahkan awak tapi saya ingin berjumpa dengan awak jadi saya memberitahu Alexander untuk menarik perhatian awak."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:196
translate malay e02s04_photo_21dcdaaf:

    # mc "Sounds a little strange, Angela."
    mc "Kedengarannya agak pelik, Angela."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:199
translate malay e02s04_photo_c7769a77:

    # atp "I will admit to being slightly flustered. It's uh... it's not easy for me... just."
    atp "Saya akan mengakui sedikit terkebil-kebil. Ia uh... Ia bukan mudah untuk saya..."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:200
translate malay e02s04_photo_85e3c151:

    # atp "I think it's better if I show you."
    atp "Saya rasa lebih baik saya tunjukkan kepada awak."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:208
translate malay e02s04_photo_c7c41f08:

    # mh "Peas in a pod, hmmm?"
    mh "Pelanduk dua serupa, hmmm?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:211
translate malay e02s04_photo_9c8529b9:

    # atp "Haha. Yeah. So, do you mind if we chat?"
    atp "Haha. Yeah. Jadi, awak tak keberatan kalau kita berbual?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:214
translate malay e02s04_photo_139c290f:

    # mh "Yes. But why don't we start fresh? I am Lyssa and this is my boyfriend, [mcname]."
    mh "Ya. Tapi kenapa kita tak mulakan semula? Saya Lyssa dan ini teman lelaki saya, [mcname]."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:217
translate malay e02s04_photo_15e5860b:

    # atp "Lyssa, [mcname]. Nice."
    atp "Lyssa, [mcname]. Bagus."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:218
translate malay e02s04_photo_67fb70ba:

    # atp "I'm Angela, and you know my husband, Alexander."
    atp "Saya Angela, dan awak kenal suami saya, Alexander."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:220
translate malay e02s04_photo_87655d2c:

    # ap "Pleasure, and thanks for being so understanding."
    ap "Seronok, dan terima kasih kerana begitu memahami."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:234
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_af7148fc:

    # atp "So your assistant knows and you've told many of the people at the courthouse... and they don't care?"
    atp "Jadi pembantu awak tahu dan awak dah beritahu ramai orang di mahkamah... Dan mereka tak kisah?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:237
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_8ee9cd18:

    # mh "Correct."
    mh "Betul."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:240
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_20d2e621:

    # atp "How do they not care? I've had people just give me blank stares when I told them."
    atp "Macam mana mereka tak peduli? Saya ada orang yang hanya beri saya pandangan kosong bila saya memberitahu mereka."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:241
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_e4778d74:

    # atp "Some days I wish I kept it a secret. Some people started acting different to me at work."
    atp "Beberapa hari saya berharap saya merahsiakannya. Sesetengah orang mula bertindak berbeza dengan saya di tempat kerja."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:242
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_ea300e24:

    # atp "I'm one of the most accomplished executives at Channel Six. Not just in the company, but in the industry..."
    atp "Saya salah seorang eksekutif paling berjaya di Saluran Enam. Bukan sahaja dalam syarikat, tapi dalam industri..."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:243
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_3aa7a0f8:

    # atp "... but I'm still just known as the \"Stallion\"."
    atp "{w}Tapi saya masih dikenali sebagai \"Stallion\"."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:246
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_ad95afc1:

    # mh "I admire your bravery for putting yourself out there. I... My only advice would be to do your best to tune out the idiots."
    mh "Saya mengagumi keberanian awak untuk meletakkan diri awak di sana. Saya... Satu-satunya nasihat saya ialah lakukan yang terbaik untuk menyingkirkan orang-orang bodoh itu."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:247
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_df2927f3:

    # mh "I know that is not easy. As more people accept you, more people learn about you, and more idiots come out of the woodwork."
    mh "Saya tahu itu bukan mudah. Bila lebih ramai orang menerima awak, lebih ramai orang belajar tentang awak, dan lebih ramai orang bodoh keluar dari situ."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:250
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_398f637e:

    # atp "Getting to open up about it feels good. And I appreciate you being, uh... {w}being patient with me."
    atp "Bercakap tentang perkara itu terasa baik. Dan saya menghargai awak, uh... {w}sabar dengan saya."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:252
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_ba76b91e:

    # mh "Water under the bridge, my dear."
    mh "Yang lepas jangan dikenang, sayang."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:255
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_dd3767f7:

    # mc "So how did you two get together?"
    mc "Jadi macam mana kamu berdua berjumpa?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:258
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_5c7ffc4b:

    # ap "We met in college, both working on our journalism degrees. And we've been together ever since."
    ap "Kami bertemu di kolej, kedua-duanya ambil ijazah kewartawanan kami. Dan kami telah bersama sejak itu."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:261
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_03ffe92b:

    # mc "Working together in the same place. That's got to be nice."
    mc "Bekerja bersama di tempat yang sama. Itu pasti bagus."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:264
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_f9ab9b36:

    # ap "Uh-yeah. It's very nice. Lot of fun."
    ap "Uh-yeah. Ia sangat bagus. Seronok sangat."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:267
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_78ac8cc7:

    # mc "So she makes the show run but you lead the show right?"
    mc "Jadi dia membuat persembahan itu berjalan tapi awak mengetuai rancangan itu, kan?"

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:270
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_56d100ce:

    # ap "Haha. You're very kind. With all the grit and effort that goes into it, it {i}looks{/i} like I run the show, but I just put my spin on whatever is on the teleprompter."
    ap "Haha. Awak sangat baik hati. Dengan segala kesungguhan dan usaha yang dilakukan, ia {i}nampaknya{/i} macam saya menjalankan rancangan itu, tapi saya hanya letakkan putaran saya pada apa sahaja yang ada pada teleprompter."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:271
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_47e7a8fa:

    # ap "Well, my spin and my voice."
    ap "Jadi, putaran saya dan suara saya."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:274
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_7dfe218c:

    # mc "You kind of sound like everyone else."
    mc "Awak bunyi macam orang lain."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:277
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_37d1f220:

    # ap "That's because I didn't turn on my \"newsreader voice\"."
    ap "Itu sebab saya tak menghidupkan \"suara pembaca berita\" saya."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:280
translate malay e02s04_fireplace_e3956977:

    # mc "Woah. You like... it's almost like you turned into a different person. Not bad."
    mc "Woah. Awak macam... Ia hampir macam awak bertukar menjadi orang yang berbeza. Boleh tahan."

# game/code/e02/e02s04.rpy:283
